{"tid":1202984,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"石禮謙!石田為業喜非常?","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T11:11:25.000Z","uid":68930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b20fbc5c6bd948515173f845317f5b69cf3b6e4","tid":1202984,"uid":68930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:08:06.000Z","msg":"儘管董事會中的大多數持有不同看法，但董事會主席潘蘇通強烈表示，近期發生的社會矛盾和經濟不穩定不會對香港商業地產市場的長期發展有所影響。惟包括石禮謙在內6名董事局成員認為，近期發生的社會矛盾和經濟不穩定將可對香港商業地產市場的增長產生負面影響，故投票贊成該事項的決議案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190611/59703606?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyatm&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190611%2F59703606%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyatm%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=637b69d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190611%2F59703606%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyatm%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=210772b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190611/59703606?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyatm&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"3ac54d3672272809f2040e4625229bf937c87977","tid":1202984,"uid":68930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"石仔做乜冇信心"},{"pid":"42e009babb0accdafb222888579d4ad4561bd814","tid":1202984,"uid":68930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:09:33.000Z","msg":"石仔邊句先係真"},{"pid":"3b85061ad2c7805ccbab0efc907afafac05eb119","tid":1202984,"uid":68930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201